1.1.name: wordpress/funny-photos
1.1.description: Plugin "Funny Photos" displays Funny photos on your blog. There are over 5,000 photos. Add Funny Photos to your sidebar on your blog using a widget. Photos are saved on our database, so you don't need to have space for all that information.
